data.description: Get into a new home just in time for the holidays! This north facing Highland Home with 5 beds, 4 baths, study and game room at 3,437 sf is PRICED TO SELL! Features include spacious and inviting open floor plan with two story foyer. Oversized primary bedroom with large en suite bath plus additional guest suite downstairs! Private study and formal dining provide perfect spaces for work and entertainment. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's delight featuring granite countertops, built-in gas range, and breakfast area. Upstairs are three secondary rooms, two full baths, and game room providing ample space to relax and unwind. Step outside onto the covered patio that leads to a private backyard. Tons of extra storage space with 3 attics & 2 large storage closets. Energy Star Certified + Radiant Barrier. Easy access to 380, 75, & DNT. 7 miles to historic Downtown McKinney and less than 5 miles to the new McKinney H-E-B and future Whole Foods Market.
